WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:04.000
♪♪

00:04.169 --> 00:05.395
C'mon!

00:07.536 --> 00:08.544
All set!

00:10.935 --> 00:12.701
Next stop, Monacrow!

00:12.778 --> 00:14.115
Home to EX.C.E.S.S.,

00:14.192 --> 00:17.810
the EXtreme Consumer Electronics
and Science Symposium!

00:17.887 --> 00:19.099
Experimental race cars!

00:19.176 --> 00:20.208
Lasers!

00:20.286 --> 00:21.810
- Airplanes?
- You bet, old friend.

00:21.887 --> 00:24.810
And Monacrow is said to be
the final resting place

00:24.887 --> 00:27.066
of the elusive
Maltese MacGuffin!

00:27.143 --> 00:29.038
Lost during Netherworld War II,

00:29.115 --> 00:31.560
this ephemeral heirloom
is so rare

00:31.637 --> 00:34.427
that no one has ever
laid eyes upon it.

00:34.504 --> 00:36.712
Whoa. So what
is it exactly?

00:36.789 --> 00:39.701
The stuff dreams are made of.

00:40.239 --> 00:42.435
No, but, like,
is it a statue or...

00:43.801 --> 00:44.951
Come on, Uncle Donald!

00:45.028 --> 00:46.497
You can fix the houseboat
when we get back.

00:46.574 --> 00:48.443
Uh-uh. I'm almost done.

00:48.520 --> 00:51.490
We'll be on the water
again in two days!

00:51.567 --> 00:53.035
Aak!

00:53.345 --> 00:54.896
Seven days!

00:58.161 --> 01:00.270
I should get started.

01:01.105 --> 01:02.905
No rush!

01:03.104 --> 01:05.123
Granny?
You're coming too?!

01:05.200 --> 01:07.387
I have 987 vacation days
saved up,

01:07.464 --> 01:10.388
and Monacrow's Blackwater
Beaches are legendary.

01:10.465 --> 01:12.232
It's high time
I "wilded out"

01:12.309 --> 01:15.693
with some "maxing"
and "relaxing," hmm?

01:15.770 --> 01:17.666
I have
the coolest grandma.

01:17.743 --> 01:20.167
Sure. Now
who's ready for the...

01:20.244 --> 01:21.620
♪ Best road trip ever! ♪

01:21.697 --> 01:23.122
♪ Best road trip ever! ♪

01:23.199 --> 01:24.676
Oh!
You'll get it.

01:25.479 --> 01:27.341
Six months ago,
if you'd have told me

01:27.418 --> 01:29.282
I should take in
a group of youngins...

01:29.359 --> 01:31.574
- I did.
- I woulda called ya daft.

01:31.651 --> 01:32.763
But I tell you,

01:32.840 --> 01:36.387
I haven't felt this energized
and vital since...

01:36.603 --> 01:38.855
Well, a long time.

01:38.939 --> 01:40.746
Load up, everyone!

01:41.459 --> 01:43.199
Psst! Psst! Hey!

01:45.213 --> 01:46.715
Did you get it?

01:47.258 --> 01:49.195
Come on, kids!

01:50.120 --> 01:52.536
To our greatest adventure
yet!

01:52.613 --> 01:55.245
Whooo! To adventure!

01:57.000 --> 02:03.074
-= www.OpenSubtitles.org =-

